snippet.title: Let's Play Enemy Zero- Part 4: And then everything really starts to suck
snippet.description: It's time for this game to be over and for everyone to bask in the glory that is the finale of Enemy Zero. All questions will be answered, all loves will be fulfilled, and everything will collapse in on itself for a singularity of shit that you wouldn't believe.
